https://lihkg.com/thread/1716586/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1720530/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1720530/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KP62qfC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKP62qfC.gif&h=21957c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cab96053a454292eea8609895f9143814169dcd1","tid":1722561,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"我諗佢成世人都未來過香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928e3a792842298cb203ae12e433d3d2f08351ef","tid":1722561,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">存款在英國，子女在英國怎麼表態？這叫公務員素質高？這樣的素質有什麼用？</span><br />\n暗示緊習帝?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f32926d9df650d5eca9202aa71f01d142a14752","tid":1722561,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"不過帶林鄭返你屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd01569efd21437edf9b14cf2f570a67cbebe97","tid":1722561,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:22.000Z","msg":"無人識你呀"},{"pid":"9b89519a4d8c17768d3ddd09a28ac99d49dfaf3c","tid":1722561,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">金一南指要等香港的問題充分暴露出來，教育很多大陸人，不僅一般民眾，甚至領導層、領導同志都有過的「不很正確的認識」。</span><br />\n<br />\ntrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b31aa71318c1dd0c5cbb01e2e5eabd8e5730e1","tid":1722561,"uid":245713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c37ddf90e3691a8015246ca41ece4ff95017b19","tid":1722561,"uid":79655,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"